{"tid":143252,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GiGi 簡 單 為 女 兒 賀 生 日","createTime":"2017-03-04T13:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T14:12:04.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"daf64b4378e490e983fc4179e553156fd8b64f82","tid":143252,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪（GiGi）前晚為囡囡Sofia慶祝兩歲生日，今年生日過得很低調，僅邀請至親同好友出席，當然GiGi媽咪與經理人都有到。GiGi送了兩本童話故事書給囡囡，因為Sofia喜歡看書，而且老公Sergio每晚都會在睡前讀故事給Sofia聽。<br />\n<br />\nGiGi昨日在網上貼出抱着Sofia的相片，留言：「簡單的DIY佈置、朋友親手做的蛋糕、加上一些親朋好友，Sofia慶祝兩歲生日。平安喜樂！感恩滿足！P.S.謝謝小美姐送給Sofia的衫仔裙仔。」從照片看Sofia生日會以粉紅搭配白色的簡單佈置，蛋糕上有Elmo與Sofia卡通糖霜公仔，Sofia收到蛋糕，相當開心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170302/large/02ec3p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170302%2Flarge%2F02ec3p7.jpg&h=19c2d1d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGiGi囡囡Sofia前晚慶祝生日，收到卡通糖霜蛋糕。"},{"pid":"a2bedf425181a54657a36acea90aae91d75a3b2c","tid":143252,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西</span></span>"},{"pid":"1b49f284cfbcc0c075bf623e3e231be2f30df28b","tid":143252,"uid":63623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"西班牙籍老公Sergio的中國籍老婆GiGi簡單為中西混血女兒賀生日"},{"pid":"3e5c87b8f3bc52cbba849c283561e3ee3b25af58","tid":143252,"uid":14130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">班</span></span>"},{"pid":"0aea47dc6108595bdcf3f35af250c757b4f4e3ae","tid":143252,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span st